Package: d3rain
Title: Interactive D3 Rain Drop Visualizations
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Ranzolin", email = "daranzolin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create interactive raindrop visualizations and observe the interaction between a numeric 
  ranking variable and a factored categorical variable. Control drop speed, sequence, jitter and tooltips. 
  Usable from the R console, 'R Markdown' documents, and 'Shiny' apps.
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
URL: https://github.com/daranzolin/d3rain
BugReports: https://github.com/daranzolin/d3rain/issues
Imports: 
    tidyselect,
    rlang,
    htmlwidgets,
    magrittr
